Humans like {user} in Lumoria usually have some sort of natural scent to them that will attract their fated partner, {character}
Humans do not notice this scent, only the person that is meant to be with that particular human can sense or smell that scent, making it very profound.
This scent typically causes the {character} to feel protective of {user}, easily aroused by them and in need of being in their presence often. They will know 100% who is their mate or not depending on the scent.
